          <h2 class="subtitle font-size-1 line-height-5 font-weight-1 letter-space-1 text-left" style="color: #ffffff;font-Family: 'Nanum Gothic',Dotum,sans-serif;">2019. 12. 14&nbsp;<br>팬미팅 [이달의 소녀 PREMIER GREETING : Meet&amp;Up] 개최 (서울)&nbsp;<br>The fan meeting [LOOΠΔ PREMIER GREETING : Meet&amp;Up] was held (Seoul)&nbsp;<br><br>2019. 12. 13&nbsp;<br>이달의 소녀 리드 싱글 '365' 발매&nbsp;<br>LOOΠΔ's lead single '365' was released<br><br>2019. 11. 26<br>2019 아시아 아티스트 어워즈 인 베트남 / 포커스상 가수 부문, 스타15 인기상<br>2019 Asia Artist Award in Vietnam / Focus-Singer Award, Star15 Popularity Award<br><br>2019. 08. 22<br>2019 소리바다 베스트 케이뮤직 어워드 / 퍼포먼스 부문<br>2019 Soribada Best K-Music Awards / Performance Award<br><br>2019. 07. 18<br>2019 MTN 방송광고 페스티벌 / CF스타 신인상<br>2019 MTN Ad Festival Awards / CF Star Rookies<br><br>2019. 02. 19<br>이달의 소녀 리팩키지 앨범 [X X] 발매<br>LOOΠΔ's repackage album [X X] was released<br><br>2019. 02. 16 - 2018. 02. 17<br>이달의 소녀 콘서트 [LOOΠΔVERSE] 개최 (서울)<br>LOOΠΔ's concert [LOOΠΔVERSE] was held (Seoul)<br><br>2018. 12. 19<br>2019 대한민국 퍼스트브랜드 대상 / 여자 신인 아이돌 부문<br><br>2018. 11. 23 - 2018. 11. 25<br>보이는 라디오 콘서트 [LOOΠΔ Studio in Seoul] 개최 (서울)<br>LOOΠΔ's visual radio concert [LOOΠΔ Studio in Seoul] was held (Seoul)<br><br>2018. 11. 04<br>MTV Europe Music Awards / Best Korean Act<br><br>2018. 08. 20<br>이달의 소녀 미니 앨범 [+ +] 발매<br>LOOΠΔ's first mini album [+ +] was released<br><br>2018. 08. 19<br>데뷔 콘서트 [LOOΠΔbirth] 개최 (서울)<br>LOOΠΔ's debut concert [LOOΠΔbirth] was held (Seoul)<br><br>2018. 08. 07<br>이달의 소녀 리드 싱글 'favOriTe' 발매<br>LOOΠΔ's lead single 'favOriTe' was released<br><br>2018. 07. 07<br>뮤직비디오 상영회 [이달의 소녀 Cinema Theory 'Up&amp;Line' in Busan] 개최 (부산)<br>The music video screening event [LOOΠΔ Cinema Theory 'Up&amp;Line' in Busan] was held (Busan)<br><br>2018. 06. 02 - 2018. 06. 03<br>팬미팅 [이달의 소녀 PREMIER GREETING : Line&amp;Up] 개최 (서울)<br>The fan meeting [LOOΠΔ PREMIER GREETING : Line&amp;Up] was held (Seoul)<br><br>2018. 05. 30<br>이달의 소녀 yyxy 미니 앨범 [beauty&amp;thebeat] 발매<br>LOOΠΔ/yyxy's first mini album [beauty&amp;thebeat] was released<br><br>2018. 03. 30<br>Olivia Hye 싱글 앨범 [Olivia Hye],&nbsp;[Go Won&amp;Olivia Hye] 발매<br>The twelfth single [Olivia Hye] was released<br><br>2018. 03. 17<br>뮤직비디오 상영회 [이달의 소녀 Cinema Theory 'Up&amp;Line'] 개최 (서울)<br>The music video screening event [LOOΠΔ Cinema Theory 'Up&amp;Line'] was held (Seoul)<br><br>2018. 03. 17<br>열 두번째 멤버 "Olivia Hye" 공개<br>The twelfth member Olivia Hye was revealed<br><br>2018. 02. 03<br>뮤직비디오 상영회 [이달의 소녀 X 심화학습반] 개최 (서울)<br>The music video screening event [LOOΠΔ X Study Group] was held (Seoul) 1st LOOΠΔ X Study Group<br><br>2018. 01. 30<br>고원 싱글 앨범 [Go Won],&nbsp;[Chuu&amp;Go Won] 발매<br>The eleventh single [Go Won],&nbsp;[Chuu&amp;Go Won] was released<br><br>2018. 01. 15<br>열한 번째 멤버 "고원" 공개<br>The eleventh member Go Won was revealed<br><br>2017. 12. 28<br>츄 싱글 앨범 [Chuu], [Yves&amp;Chuu] 발매<br>The tenth single [Chuu],&nbsp;[Yves&amp;Chuu] was released<br><br>2017. 12. 14<br>열 번째 멤버 "츄" 공개<br>The tenth member Chuu was revealed<br><br>2017. 11. 28<br>이브 싱글 앨범 [Yves] 발매<br>The ninth single [Yves] was released<br><br>2017. 11. 14<br>아홉 번째 멤버 "이브" 공개<br>The ninth member Yves was revealed<br><br>2017. 10. 31<br>이달의 소녀 오드아이써클 리팩키지 앨범 [Max&amp;Match] 발매<br>LOOΠΔ / ODD EYE CIRCLE's repackage album [Max&amp;Match] was released<br><br>2017. 09. 21<br>이달의 소녀 오드아이써클 미니 앨범 [Mix&amp;Match] 발매<br>LOOΠΔ / ODD EYE CIRCLE's first mini album [Mix&amp;Match] was released<br><br>2017. 07. 28<br>최리 싱글 앨범 [Choerry], [JinSoul&amp;Choerry] 발매<br>The eighth single [Choerry], [JinSoul&amp;Choerry] were released<br><br>2017. 07. 12<br>여덟 번째 멤버 "최리" 공개<br>The eighth member Choerry was revealed<br><br>2017. 06. 26<br>진솔 싱글 앨범 [JinSoul], [Kim Lip&amp;JinSoul] 발매<br>The seventh single [JinSoul], [Kim Lip&amp;JinSoul] were released<br><br>2017. 06. 13<br>일곱 번째 멤버 "진솔" 공개<br>The seventh member JinSoul was revealed<br><br>2017. 05. 26<br>김립 싱글 앨범 [Kim Lip] 오프라인 발매<br>The sixth single [Kim Lip] was released physically<br><br>2017. 05. 23<br>김립 싱글 앨범 [Kim Lip] 온라인 발매<br>The sixth single [Kim Lip] was released digitally<br><br>2017. 05. 15<br>여섯 번째 멤버 "김립" 공개<br>The sixth member Kim Lip was revealed<br><br>2017. 04. 27<br>이달의 소녀 1/3 리팩키지 앨범 [Love&amp;Evil] 발매<br>LOOΠΔ 1/3's repackage mini album [Love&amp;Evil] was released<br><br>2017. 04. 17<br>ViVi 싱글 앨범 [ViVi], [HaSeul&amp;ViVi] 발매<br>The fifith single [ViVi],&nbsp;[HaSeul&amp;ViVi] was released<br><br>2017. 03. 13<br>이달의 소녀 1/3 미니 앨범 [Love&amp;Live] 발매<br>LOOΠΔ 1/3's first mini album [Love&amp;Live] was released<br><br>2017. 02. 13<br>다섯 번째 멤버 "ViVi" 공개<br>The fifth member ViVi was revealed<br><br>2017. 1. 16<br>여진 싱글 앨범 [YeoJin], [HaSeul&amp;YeoJin], [LOOΠΔ&amp;YeoJin] 발매<br>The fourth single albums [YeoJin], [HaSeul&amp;YeoJin], and [LOOΠΔ&amp;YeoJin] were released<br><br>2017. 01. 04<br>네 번째 멤버 "여진" 공개<br>The fourth member YeoJin was revealed<br><br>2016. 12. 15<br>하슬 싱글 [HaSeul], [LOOΠΔ&amp;HaSeul] 발매<br>The third single albums [HaSeul] and [LOOΠΔ&amp;HaSeul] were released<br><br>2016. 12. 08<br>세 번째 멤버 "하슬" 공개<br>The third member HaSeul was revealed<br><br>2016. 11. 17<br>현진 싱글 앨범 [HyunJin], [HeeJin&amp;HyunJin] 발매<br>The second single albums [HyunJin] and [HeeJin&amp;HyunJin] were released<br><br>2016. 10. 28<br>두 번째 멤버 "현진" 공개<br>The second member HyunJin was revealed<br><br>2016. 10. 05<br>희진 싱글 앨범 [HeeJin] 발매<br>The first single album [HeeJin] was released<br><br>2016. 09. 26<br>이달의 소녀(LOOΠΔ) 첫 멤버 "희진" 공개<br>The first member HeeJin was revealed<br><br></h2> 
